svn:log
V 830
Added the functions 'nmg_plot_fu', 'nmg_triangulate_rm_holes', 'nmg_triangulate_rm_degen_loopuse', and 'nmg_dump_model' to the file 'nmg_tri.c'. These are prototype functions that support the new prototype function 'nmg_triangulate_fu' (nmg triangulate faceuse). The function 'nmg_plot_fu' creates a plot file for each loopuse in a faceuse and color codes each edgeuse. The function 'nmg_triangulate_rm_holes' removes holes (OT_OPPOSITE loopuse) in a faceuse by joining them with outer loops (OT_SAME loopuse). The function 'nmg_triangulate_rm_degen_loopuse' removes degenerate (i.e. < 3 vertices) loopuse from a faceuse. The function 'nmg_dump_model' write all the vertex coordinates in an nmg model to a log file. Preprocessor commands were added so these new functions are disabled by default. This code is a work in progress.

END
